WEBVTT

00:00:06.389 --> 00:00:08.055
When faced with a big challenge

00:00:08.055 --> 00:00:11.336
where potential failure seems
to lurk at every corner,

00:00:11.336 --> 00:00:14.228
maybe you've heard this advice before:

00:00:14.228 --> 00:00:16.419
"Be more confident."

00:00:16.419 --> 00:00:19.530
And most likely, this is what you think
when you hear it:

00:00:19.530 --> 00:00:22.261
"If only it were that simple."

00:00:22.261 --> 00:00:24.322
But what is confidence?

00:00:24.322 --> 00:00:28.086
Take the belief that you are valuable,
worthwhile, and capable,

00:00:28.086 --> 00:00:30.136
also known as self-esteem,